00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:33.600
[Amit Varma]: Xi Jinping, the president of the People's Republic of China and Narendra Modi, the Prime

00:02:33.600 --> 00:02:37.120
[Amit Varma]: Minister of India, met recently at Mammalapuram.

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:42.080
[Amit Varma]: Besides the feel good quotes and the photo op in front of a giant rock that did not turn

